# Live Google Maps via the web provider (BrowserComponent + Maps JS): tiles,
# labels and road data load from Google and shift run-to-run, and the JS API
# re-lays labels more freely than a native map, so the tolerance is wide. It
# still fails loudly on a blank / blocked map or a failed key (which differs
# across essentially the whole frame) -- the regression this test guards.
maxChannelDelta=40
maxMismatchPercent=35.0
